  "title": "Add `pushStateObject` to get Turbolinks compatibility",
  "body": "This PR aims to fix #985 and get Turbolinks compatibility by setting `pushStateObject: { turbolinks: true }`.\n\nYou may reproduce the problem described by @ThomasBush on http://www.welcometothejungle.co/companies : \n- Activate some filters/facets\n- Click on whatever company\n- Go back => NOK (it doesn't work until you reach back `/companies` in the history)\n\n---\n\nsee:\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/985\n- https://github.com/turbolinks/turbolinks-classic/issues/363#issuecomment-85626145\n",
